# Code Description

Project done with Python in Jupyter notebook

# Section: Text Description and Exploration

- The structure of hate/non-hate speech is explored
- Exploration of missing values done

# Section: Text Pre-processing

- The training and test dataset are combined for pre-processing.
- The combo dataset is cleaned using regex
- The words were reduced to there base words using lemmatization and then tokenized.

# Section: Text Visualization

- The visualization is done using matplotlib and wordcloud.
- Importance of hashtags are visualized.

# Section: Training and Predicting

- After splitting the combo dataset into training and test dataset, different classification algorithms were used to predict the target variable.
- Out of all the algorithms, support vector classifier is chosen as it generated the highest score among the others.
